#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Available Quantity:</b> The amount of stock on hand that has not yet "
"been\n"
"                    reserved for delivery."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tilgængelig mængde:</b> Den mængde på lager, der endnu ikke er\n"
"                    reserveret til levering."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Connected Printer:</b> Automate label printing by connecting your\n"
"                            printer."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tilsluttet printer:</b> Automatisér etiketudskrivning ved at tilslutte "
"din\n"
"                            printer."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Create Storage Categories:</b> Define\n"
"                        categories that can be linked to the capacity of one "
"or more package\n"
"                        types."
msgstr ""
"<b>Opret opbevaringskategorier:</b> Fastlæg\n"
"                        kategorier, der kan knyttes til kapaciteten for en "
"eller flere pakketyper\n"
"                        ."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Create your stock locations:</b> Each stock\n"
"                        location can be linked to a storage category, a "
"barcode, and a removal\n"
"                        strategy. To create or update many locations at "
"once, use the built-in\n"
"                        import/export documentation and templates."
msgstr ""
"<b>Opret dine lagerplaceringer:</b> Hver lagerplacering\n"
"                        kan knyttes til en lagerkategori, en stregkode og en "
"strategi for produktudførelse.\n"
"                        For at oprette eller opdatere mange placeringer på "
"én gang skal du bruge den indbyggede\n"
"                        import-/eksportdokumentation og skabeloner."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Define your warehouse flow:</b> Update your <b>Warehouse\n"
"                        Settings</b> to choose a 1, 2, or 3-step process for "
"receiving and shipping\n"
"                        goods. This allows you to tailor the workflow to "
"your specific needs,\n"
"                        whether you prefer a simple direct transfer or a "
"more detailed multi-step\n"
"                        verification process."
msgstr ""
"<b>Definér dit lagerflow:</b> Opdatér dine <b>lagerindstillinger\n"
"                        </b> for at vælge en 1-, 2- eller 3-trins proces "
"til\n"
"                        modtagelse og forsendelse af varer. Dette giver dig "
"mulighed for at tilpasse arbejdsgangen til dine behov,\n"
"                        uanset om du foretrækker en enkel direkte overførsel "
"eller en mere detaljeret\n"
"                        proces med verifikation i flere trin."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Generate a new invoice</b> directly from the existing <b>Sales\n"
"                                    Order.</b>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Generér en ny faktura</b> direkte fra den eksisterende <b>salgsordre\n"
"                                    .</b>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Going Further!</b>"
msgstr "<b>Gå et skridt videre!</b>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>In the Contact App:</b>"
msgstr "<b>I Kontakterappen:</b>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>In the Inventory App:</b>"
msgstr "<b>I Lagerappen:</b>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Locate the customer's last invoice.</b>"
msgstr "<b>Find kundens seneste faktura.</b>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Login as:</b>"
msgstr "<b>Log ind som:</b>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Manage your package types:</b> Define all\n"
"                        the types of packages you handle (e.g., pallets, "
"boxes). These will be used\n"
"                        to create <b>Storage Categories</b>, which help you "
"optimize warehouse\n"
"                        space."
msgstr ""
"<b>Administrér dine pakketyper:</b> Definér alle\n"
"                        de pakketyper, du håndterer (f.eks. paller, kasser). "
"Disse vil blive brugt\n"
"                        til at oprette <b>lagerkategorier</b>, som hjælper "
"dig med at optimere lagerpladsen\n"
"                        ."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Manutention Report:</b> Provides details on completed transfers and\n"
"                            the number of packages created by type and the "
"quantity of products\n"
"                            delivered."
msgstr ""
"<b>Rapport om varelagring:</b> Indeholder oplysninger om gennemførte "
"overførsler,\n"
"                            herunder antallet af oprettede pakker fordelt "
"efter type samt\n"
"                            mængden af leverede produkter."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Note:</b> Storage data is updated daily, so it's not live. Be sure to\n"
"                            select a date that is not today."
msgstr ""
"<b>Bemærk: Lagerdataene</b> opdateres dagligt og er derfor ikke i realtid. "
"Vælg\n"
"                            en anden dato end i dag."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Odoo will automatically duplicate</b> the previous invoice,\n"
"                                    using the correct start date (based on "
"your defined invoice\n"
"                                    period) but setting <b>all\n"
"                                        quantity lines to\n"
"                                        zero</b>. This prevents accidental "
"overbilling and allows\n"
"                                    you to input the current period's "
"quantities accurately."
msgstr ""
"<b>Odoo duplikerer automatisk</b> den forrige faktura\n"
"                                    og anvender den korrekte startdato "
"(baseret på den faktureringsperiode, du har defineret),\n"
"                                    men <b>sætter alle\n"
"                                        mængdelinjer til\n"
"                                        nul</b>. Dette forhindrer utilsigtet "
"overfakturering og giver dig mulighed for\n"
"                                    at angive de korrekte mængder for den "
"aktuelle periode."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Open the CRM app</b> and create a new opportunity."
msgstr "<b>Åbn CRM-appen</b>, og opret en ny salgsmulighed."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Password:</b> portal"
msgstr "<b>Adgangskode:</b> portal"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Picking Optimization:</b> Optimize picking with different methods like "
"<b>Batch\n"
"                            Picking, Wave Picking,</b> and <b>Cluster "
"Picking</b>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Optimering af plukning:</b> Optimér plukningen med forskellige metoder "
"som <b>partiplukning,\n"
"                            bølgeplukning</b> og <b>klyngeplukning</b>."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Putaway Rules:</b> Customize how products are stored based on your own\n"
"                            rules."
msgstr ""
"<b>Indleveringsregler:</b> Tilpas den måde, produkterne opbevares på, i "
"henhold til dine egne\n"
"                            regler."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Quality Report:</b> Gives information on the number of quality checks\n"
"                            performed."
msgstr ""
"<b>Kvalitetsrapport:</b> Giver oplysninger om antallet af udførte\n"
"                            kvalitetskontroller."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Reserved Quantity:</b> The amount of stock that has already been "
"allocated for\n"
"                    a scheduled shipment."
msgstr ""
"<b>Reserveret mængde:</b> Den mængde lagerbeholdning, der allerede er afsat "
"til\n"
"                    en planlagt forsendelse."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Set up location-based fees:</b> In the configuration, you can define\n"
"                        different <b>Fee Rates</b> and link them to specific "
"storage locations. This\n"
"                        lets you apply different prices to various types of "
"storage, such as\n"
"                        refrigerated or high-bay areas. This granular "
"control allows for automated\n"
"                        and accurate invoicing based on the number of "
"pallets per fee rate."
msgstr ""
"<b>Opsætning af lokationsbaserede gebyrer:</b> I konfigurationen kan du "
"definere\n"
"                        forskellige <b>takster</b> og knytte dem til "
"bestemte lagerlokationer. På\n"
"                        den måde kan du anvende forskellige priser for "
"forskellige lagertyper, f.eks.\n"
"                        kølelager eller højreollager. Denne detaljerede "
"styring muliggør automatisk\n"
"                        og præcis fakturering baseret på antallet af paller "
"inden for hver takst."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Shipping Connector:</b> Connect with various carriers directly within\n"
"                            Odoo."
msgstr ""
"<b>Transportfirma:</b> Opret forbindelse til forskellige transportører "
"direkte i\n"
"                            Odoo."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Storage Report:</b> Shows the amount of packages stored per day,\n"
"                            broken down by fee rate."
msgstr ""
"<b>Lagringsrapport:</b> Viser antallet af pakker, der er lagret pr. dag,\n"
"                            opdelt efter gebyrsats."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>User:</b> portal@portal.com"
msgstr "<b>Bruger:</b> portal@portal.com"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Validate</b> the invoice."
msgstr "<b>Validér</b> fakturaen."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Validate</b> the quotation to finalize the sales order."
msgstr "<b>Validér</b> tilbuddet for at afslutte salgsordren."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Validate</b> the transfer."
msgstr "<b>Validér</b> overførslen."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Validate</b> to finalize the order."
msgstr "<b>Validér</b> for at afslutte ordren."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.ir_ui_view_2473
msgid ""
"<br/>Leverage advanced 3PL automation and real-time transparency for "
"unparalleled efficiency and competitive advantage.<br/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<br/>Udnyt avanceret 3PL-automatisering og realtidsgennemsigtighed for at "
"opnå højere effektivitet og en stærkere konkurrencefordel.<br/><br/>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<em>Example:  A category named \"5 Std Pal\" can be configured to hold\n"
"                        five standard pallets.</em>"
msgstr ""
"<em>Eksempel: En kategori med navnet »5 Std.-Pal« kan konfigureres til at "
"indeholde\n"
"                        fem standardpaller.</em>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<em>Example: A client who had 150 pallets at €0.30/day and 55 pallets at\n"
"                        €0.45/day in August.</em>"
msgstr ""
"<em>Eksempel: En kunde havde i august 150 paller til 0,30 € pr. dag og 55 "
"paller til\n"
"                        0,45 € pr. dag.</em>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Barcode App</b>:</font> Streamlines "
"warehouse floor operations by enabling\n"
"                    fast and accurate scanning of pallets, locations, and "
"stock movements."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Stregkodeapp</b>:</font> Optimerer "
"arbejdsgangene på lageret ved at muliggøre\n"
"                    hurtig og præcis scanning af paller, lagerlokationer og "
"lagerbevægelser."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>CRM App</b>:</font> Tracks leads and "
"opportunities efficiently, helping\n"
"                    logistics companies follow up on prospects and manage "
"long-term customer relationships."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>CRM-app</b>:</font> Sporer leads og "
"salgsmuligheder effektivt og hjælper\n"
"                    logistikvirksomheder med at følge op på potentielle "
"kunder og pleje langsigtede kunderelationer."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Documents App</b>:</font> Centralizes "
"contracts, delivery notes, and\n"
"                    transport documentation in a searchable digital space."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Dokumenterapp</b>:</font> Samler "
"kontrakter, leveringssedler og\n"
"                    transportdokumenter i ét søgbart digitalt miljø."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Inventory App</b>:</font> Enables precise "
"stock management across multiple\n"
"                    warehouses and clients, ensuring full tracking of "
"inbound, outbound, and internal movements."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Lagerapp</b>:</font> Gør det muligt at "
"foretage en præcis lagerstyring på tværs af flere\n"
"                    lagre og kunder og sikrer fuldstændig sporing af "
"indgående, udgående og interne bevægelser."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Invoicing App</b>:</font> Automates "
"billing calculations based on storage\n"
"                    duration, volume, and handling services, with support "
"for custom pricing per client."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Faktureringsapp</b>:</font> Automatiserer "
"faktureringen på baggrund af opbevaringstid, volumen og håndteringsydelser "
"og understøtter kundespecifikke priser."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Sales App</b>:</font> Generates "
"professional quotations and sales orders for\n"
"                    storage, transport, and value-added logistics services."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Salgsapp</b>:</font> Udarbejder "
"professionelle tilbud og salgsordrer for\n"
"\n"
"                    lagring, transport og værdiskabende logistiktjenester."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Subscriptions App</b>:</font> Manages "
"recurring billing for long-term\n"
"                    storage services with customizable plans."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Abonnementerapp</b>:</font> Administrerer "
"tilbagevendende faktureringer for langsigtede\n"
"                    lagertjenester med tilpasselige takster."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Website &amp; Portal</b>:</font> Provides "
"clients with a self-service portal\n"
"                    for real-time access to stock levels, service requests, "
"and downloadable documents."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Hjemmeside og portal</b>:</font> Tilbyder "
"kunderne en portal til selvbestilling\n"
"                    med realtidsadgang til lagerbeholdninger, "
"serviceanmodninger og dokumenter, der kan downloades."

