"control what is permitted\n"
"                        during the process. This allows you to define "
"specific rules for operations\n"
"                        like picking, ensuring the barcode functionality "
"aligns with your business\n"
"                        workflow."
msgstr ""
"Du kan tilpasse indstillingerne for hver\n"
"                        operationstype i stregkodeappen for at styre, hvad "
"der er tilladt\n"
"                        under processen. Dette giver dig mulighed for at "
"definere specifikke regler for operationer\n"
"                        som plukning, hvilket sikrer, at "
"stregkodefunktionaliteten passer til din virksomheds\n"
"                        arbejdsgang."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
